{
  "chapter": 12,
  "chapter_summary": "第十二回\"和尚弄鬼\"讲述了陆小凤与沙曼试图逃离宫九府邸的惊险经历。小玉暗中相助，命人将装有陆小凤的箱子抬回船上，却发现箱中人竟是老实和尚而非沙曼——老实和尚早已偷梁换柱。被点穴道的陆小凤随箱子被抬入船底舱，与老实和尚在黑暗中斗嘴。老实和尚解开哑穴后，两人展开一场关于\"老公鸡\"与\"小公鸡\"的机智对话，陆小凤以友情打动和尚。待船出海后，老实和尚解开穴道，陆小凤却发现箱中人已变为沙曼，二人在箱中重逢，紧紧相拥。此时有人踢箱，沙曼判断非宫九所为。陆小凤出箱查看，发现老实和尚被人吊在舱顶。正当他要放下和尚时，舱外传来脚步声，二人急忙躲回箱中。最后牛肉汤的香气飘入，暗示新的人物即将登场。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "两只小鸡、一头秃驴，若是全都老死在这里，那倒……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这箱子是谁要你们搬到这里来的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_xiang_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "抬箱子的人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "是曼姑娘。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "曼姑娘？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们是听九少爷的？还是听曼姑娘的？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们知不知道曼姑娘已经不是九少爷的人？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 45,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "抬走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "快点把这口箱子抬走。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tai_xiang_zi_de_ren",
      "speaker_name": "抬箱子的人",
      "listener": "char_xiao_yu",
      "text": "抬到哪里去？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_yu",
      "speaker_name": "小玉",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "从哪里抬来的，就抬回哪里去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是这口见鬼的箱子，害得我们想好好吃顿饭都不行。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 149
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "真他妈的活见了大头鬼。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 151,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我们倒不如索性找个没人的地方，把它扔到海里去，也免得它再作怪。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 153,
      "line_end": 153
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "可是我们至少总得看看箱子里装的究竟是些什么鬼东西？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你能开得了这把锁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 167
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "开不了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 169,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你敢把箱子砸坏？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为什么不敢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "九少爷若是问下来，谁负责任？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 175,
      "line_end": 175
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 177
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "去你娘的。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我早就知道你是个杂种。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你好像也差不多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 181,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": null,
      "listener": null,
      "text": "所以我们最好还是乖乖的把箱子抬回去，往底舱一摆就天下太平了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你这是怎么回事？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 199,
      "line_end": 199
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你千万不能死，和尚可不愿意跟个死人挤在一口箱子里。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你若想骗我，让我解开你的穴道，你就打错主意了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 209,
      "line_end": 209
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "好人不长命，祸害遗千年，我知道你死不了的。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 211,
      "line_end": 211
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我虽然不想跟你挤在箱子里打架，可是一个人自言自语也没意思，只要你乖一点，我就先解开你的哑穴。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "其实你根本不必这么做的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不必怎么做？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 233,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "不必点我的穴。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是和尚怕你生气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "为什么生气？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "小母鸡忽然变成了秃驴，小公鸡总难免生气的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "你错了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哪点错了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "小公鸡早就已经不是小公鸡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "老公鸡。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "老公鸡和小公鸡有哪点不同？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 253,
      "line_end": 253
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "有很多点，最大的一点是，老公鸡见过的母鸡，大大小小已不知有多少，却只有一个秃驴朋友。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你果然是个好朋友。",
      "tone": "感动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "其实你早就该知道的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 259,
      "line_end": 259
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在知道，还不算太迟呀。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "现在你解开我的穴道来，也不迟。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 263,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "的确不迟。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 265,
      "line_end": 265
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "虽然一点都不迟，只可惜还嫌太早了一点。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "还太早？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "太早。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 275,
      "line_end": 275
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "你准备等到什么时候？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "至少也要等到开船的时候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 279,
      "line_end": 279
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "你能不能帮我个忙？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你说。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "你能不能再把我另外一个穴道也点上一点？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 291,
      "line_end": 291
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是否气出毛病来了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你真的要我再点你一处穴道？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 297,
      "line_end": 297
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "真的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 299,
      "line_end": 299
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "什么穴？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 301,
      "line_end": 301
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "睡穴。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "看来你的运气实在不错嘛。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "text": "你还说我运气不错？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 309,
      "line_end": 309
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lao_shi_he_shang",
      "speaker_name": "老实和尚",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "至少你还有个能点你穴道的朋友，和尚却没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 311,
      "line_end": 311
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
      "speaker_name": "沙曼",
      "listener": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你终于醒过来了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lu_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "陆小凤",
      "listener": "char_sha_man",
      "text": "是你？真的是你？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 12,
      "line_start": 371,
      "line_end": 371
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sha_man",
